<div class="references-small references-column-count references-column-count-3" style="-moz-column-count:3; column-count:3;">
<ol class="references">
<li id="cite_note-norton-0">^ <a href="#cite_ref-norton_0-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-norton_0-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-norton_0-2" title=""><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <i>The Norton Anthology of English Literature</i>. Ed. Stephen Greenblatt. 8th ed. Vol. B. New York, London: W. W. Norton and Co., 2006. pp.&#160;19–21 and 160–161. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/0393928330" class="internal">ISBN 0393928330</a></li>
